        "TileImage": "$($repository db1c983c-d39c-4a8a-b7de-bfa673cccb2e).Image",
        "Description": "Welcome back 47, your target is Lance Vance now by the alias Lance Gerken a former associate of Tommy Vercetti. Once considered a loyal partner, However, Vance&apos;s betrayl led directly to Vercetti&apos;s downfall. Since then, Lance has built a reputation in the underworld as a double-dealer, switching allegiances whenever profit outweighs loyalty.\r\rEliminating Lance &amp; new found love Rosalee Sunderland will both avenge the late, great Tommy &quot;Ray Liotta&quot; Vercetti and send a clear message to others.",
